cast.overview: The true story of a brilliant but politically radical debate team coach who uses the power of words to transform a group of underdog African-American college students into a historical powerhouse that took on the Harvard elite.
cast.title: The Great Debaters

cast.overview: After a workplace shooting in New Orleans, a trial against the gun manufacturer pits lawyer Wendell Rohr against shady jury consultant Rankin Fitch, who uses illegal means to stack the jury with people sympathetic to the defense. But when juror Nicholas Easter and his girlfriend Marlee reveal their ability to sway the jury into delivering any verdict they want, a high-stakes cat-and-mouse game begins.
cast.title: Runaway Jury

details.biography: Fahnlohnee R. Harris is known for The Skeleton Key (2005), Ray (2004) and Runaway Jury (2003).
details.name: Fahnlohnee R. Harris
